text: Carmine Robert "Roby" La Mura (born 11 October 1968) is an Italian rower. He competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Italian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Italy Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:People from Pompei
